## Meta Tags
- Proper viewport meta tag
- Description and keywords
- Open Graph tags for social sharing
- Favicon and touch icons

## Performance
- Inline critical CSS
- Defer non-critical JavaScript
- Optimize for Core Web Vitals
- Minimal external resources
